## §7 Founder Stripe action (in-flight, 2026-06-10)

Founder was on the Stripe Add Product dialog creating Food Node Weekly Subscription (Option C, $0/week). Guidance given in chat and recorded here for posterity:

1. Amount: `0`
2. Billing period: Weekly
3. Click Add product
4. Copy the resulting `price_...` ID
5. From the `platform/` directory:

```
npx supabase secrets set STRIPE_PRICE_FOOD_NODE_WEEKLY=price_... --project-ref ruuxzilgmuwddcofqecc
```

This unblocks Wave C PRE-2. No further steps needed until Mnemosyne is back up.

